title.narrative: Expert humanitarian specialist support to respond to the Syria/Iraq crisis.

description.narrative: This activity (Expert humanitarian specialist support to respond to the Syria/Iraq crisis.) is a component of Provision of Technical Assistance to the Syria Crisis Response reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Humanitarian assistance' and a budget of £7,739,018. This component benefits Middle East, regional, and works in the following sector(s): Relief co-ordination and support services. The start date is 05-10-2015 and the end date is 31-03-2023.
